d_media_url":"","jetpack_shortlink":"https:\/\/wp.me\/p95VHY-9EG","jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"jetpack-related-posts":[{"id":24459,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2017\/02\/26\/dua-leaving-bathroom\/","url_meta":{"origin":37118,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Dua: Supplication for leaving the lavatory","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"February 26, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas ibn Malik reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, would say upon leaving the washroom, \u201cAll praise is due to Allah, who has removed harm from me and granted me wellness.\u201d Source: Sunan Ibn Ma\u0304jah 301 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Suyuti \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0633\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0645\u064e\u0627\u0644\u0650\u0643\u064d \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":24171,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2016\/12\/14\/hamdulillah-food-drink-islam\/","url_meta":{"origin":37118,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Eating: All praise to Allah who provided for us","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 14, 2016","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Sa\u2019id reported: When the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, ate or drank, he would say, \u201cAll praise is due to Allah who has fed us, given us drink, and has made us Muslims.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 3457 Grade: Hasan (fair) according to Ibn Hajar \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0633\u064e\u0639\u0650\u064a\u062f\u064d\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627