0},"classes":[]},{"id":33925,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2020\/01\/13\/dua-rising-from-ruku\/","url_meta":{"origin":37118,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Salat: The Prophet\u2019s supplication rising from bowing","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 13, 2020","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Abi Awfa reported: When the Messegner of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, raised his back from bowing, he would say, \u201cAllah has heard one who praised Him. O Allah, our Lord, to You belong praise as fills the heavens, fills the earth, and fills anything You will\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":32274,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/06\/18\/doors-of-khayr-plentiful\/","url_meta":{"origin":37118,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Charity: Doors of virtuous good deeds are plentiful","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 18, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Dharr reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThere is no soul in the son of Adam but that charity is due upon it on every day the sun rises.\u201d It was said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, from what can we give in charity?\u201d\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/37118","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.c